# PII Patterns Configuration Template
# ====================================
# Copy this file to .pii-patterns and customize with your patterns.
#
# Usage:
#   cp .pii-patterns.example .pii-patterns
#   # Edit .pii-patterns with your personal patterns
#
# Add regex patterns (one per line) to detect in commits.
# Lines starting with # are comments.
# Patterns are case-insensitive.
#
# These patterns will block commits if found in staged files
# or in the git author name/email.

# Name patterns (uncomment and adjust)
# ------------------------------------
# firstname\.lastname
# firstname
# lastname

# Machine/hostname patterns
# -------------------------
# myhostname
# \.local$

# Username patterns
# -----------------
# myusername

# Email domain patterns
# ---------------------
# @mydomain\.com

# Address patterns (street names, etc.)
# -------------------------------------
# 123.*main.*street
